In the MATTER OF HAZARDOUS DISCHARGE SITE REMEDIATION FUND PUBLIC ENTITY GRANT APPLICATION FOR REMEDIAL INVESTIGATION AND REMEDIAL ACTION. (Barry Rosengarten - Petitioner) C-545 September Term 2018
081876 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 25, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004439-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
